    "Moreover, AI-driven platforms can offer personalized loan options and auto loan plans by understanding individual financial situations and preferences, thereby enhancing customer satisfaction and loyalty.In addition to data breaches, legal risks cannot be ignored.",
    "Historically, the revision of laws and regulations has often lagged behind the application of new technologies.",
    "At present, artificial intelligence technology also has the potential to generate false content due to data and algorithmic errors, and to some extent to discriminate against users.",
    "[2][3][4] Once the large model generates inaccurate financial risk control reports, it will be difficult to distinguish between the unreliable technology provided by technology companies and the unreliable data provided by financial institutions, making it difficult to define legal responsibilities and prone to the phenomenon of financial institutions and technology companies fighting each other.This paper examines the current state of development of AI-driven technology and the existing problems and challenges of financial risk prediction services.",
